{
  "stem": "8703.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They risked their life in order to save the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say among the silent majority, Franklin Delano Roosevelt's administration had a front place among them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were silent, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why do I hold that against that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why do I mention it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the Roosevelt administration had a chance to say something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't mean to, to just to do something drastically.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If they would say just for the Germans, we know what you are doing to the Jewish people over there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why are you killing innocent people and children, innocent children, innocent people?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If he-- you know, the Germans would take this under consideration because they didn't like it's effect, like I told you before.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They created a model camp in Theresienstadt to show the world how they are treating the people, the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was only one spot, not more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The rest were killing, killings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If Roosevelt would say, stop the killings, that's all I was asking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't do that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you will continue, you will pay for it dearly, to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the administration didn't do a thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even before the war, when England agreed to take several thousand children from Germany, Belgium did, and France, and many places.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you know that the United States didn't take in not even a single child?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When a boat came, and they wanted to come into the United States, they ran away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The United States wouldn't let them in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot the name of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just on the tip of my tongue. 907 people that the United States didn't agree to let them in even.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later a transport of 500 people, they came from Germany that they saved themselves.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
